	updated my affiliation to include CNRS and Univ. Paris-Saclay

	* src/ClusterSequence.cc (print_banner):
	updated banner so it mentions GPL v2 or higher

	* configure.ac:
	* include/fastjet/config_win.h:
	* Doxyfile:
	* tex/fastjet-doc.tex:
	  changed version to 3.3.3-devel

