2018-09-26  Gregory Soyez  <soyez@fastjet.fr>

	* NEWS:
	drafted NEWS for 3.3.2 release

	* plugins/GridJet/Makefile.am:
	* plugins/D0RunICone/Makefile.am:
	* plugins/CMSIterativeCone/Makefile.am:
	* plugins/Jade/Makefile.am:
	* plugins/EECambridge/Makefile.am:
	* plugins/ATLASCone/Makefile.am:
	* plugins/TrackJet/Makefile.am:
	* plugins/NestedDefs/Makefile.am:
	* plugins/D0RunIICone/Makefile.am:
	* plugins/PxCone/Makefile.am:
	* plugins/CDFCones/Makefile.am:
	* plugins/SISCone/Makefile.am:
	made all the lib<plugin_name>Plugin (non-monolithic build) depend
	on libfastjet

	* plugins/SISCone/Makefile.am:
	added a dependence of the produced library (single or monolithic)
	on libsiscone and libsisconespherical

	* plugins/Makefile.am:
	made libfastjetplugin (and all the individual plugin libs for
	non-monolithic biulds) depend on libfastjet

2018-09-19  Gregory Soyez  <soyez@fastjet.fr>

	* tools/Makefile.am (libfastjettools_la_LIBADD):
	made libfastjettools depend on libfastjet (issue raised by
	Jan Strube <jstrube@uoregon.edu>)

