	* NEWS
        * Doxyfile
        * configure.ac
        * doc/fastjet-doc.tex
	* include/fastjet/config_win.h
	preparing for 3.3.1 release

	* COPYING:
	changed initial paragraph to indicate that FJ license is GPL v2 or
	later (rather than just v2), in accord with the headers of the
	source files.

2018-04-22  Gavin Salam  <gavin.salam@cern.ch>

	* various/(*.hh|cc)
	* scripts/preamble-fjcore.txt:
	* scripts/update-headers.pl:
	better at handling cases where copyright is a single year (though
	it could end up reading 2018-2018); also now handles the C++ files
	in the fortran_wrapper directory; and recognises fjcore files,
	leaving the fjcore indicator in there. It also updates the
	preamble-fjcore file.

	* **/*.cc **/*.hh:
	* scripts/preamble-fjcore.txt:
	updated copyright date on FJ files to 2018

2018-04-21  Gavin Salam  <gavin.salam@cern.ch>

	* fortran_wrapper/fastjetfortran.cc:
	commented out changes that help with thread safety in
	fastjetfortran. (Plan for future is to introduce an ifdef)

2017-09-26  Gregory Soyez  <soyez@fastjet.fr>

	* m4/CGAL.m4:
	removed debugging comment

	* configure.ac:
	remove unused CGAL variable

	* m4/CGAL.m4:
	revamped the CGAL detection script to also search for libraries in
	lib64 and lib32 subdirectories when CGAL (or Boost for CGAL_ paths
	are supplied by the user

	Cleaned unused bits in the process

2017-09-18  Gregory Soyez  <soyez@fastjet.fr>

	* include/fastjet/PseudoJet.hh:
	fixed issue + added safegards for the computation of theta and
	cos_theta

2017-09-08  Gregory Soyez  <soyez@fastjet.fr>

	* NEWS:
	started drafting a NEWS for 3.4.0(?)

	* PseudoJet.hh:
	added theta() and cos_theta() PseudoJet member functions as
	well as theta(pja, pjb) and cos_theta(pja,pjb) functions

	* m4/CGAL.m4 (ACX_CHECK_CGAL):
	added an option --with-cgal-boostdir to allow specifying a
	non-standard Boost installation path used to install CGAL

2017-08-31  Gavin Salam  <gavin.salam@cern.ch>

	* plugins/SISCone/SISConeBasePlugin.cc:
	fixed erroneous UserScaleBase::StructureType -> UserScaleBase as
	reported by attila.krasznahorkay@cern.ch.

2017-08-02  Gregory Soyez  <soyez@fastjet.fr>

	* include/fastjet/JetDefinition.hh:
	fixed typo in comment

2017-07-12  Gregory Soyez  <soyez@fastjet.fr>

