        * src/Error.cc
	modified the guard to LimitedWarning Error::_execinfo_undefined;
	so that it's the same that is now used elsewhere and in Error,hh,
	i.e. #if (!defined(FASTJET_HAVE_EXECINFO_H)) || defined(__FJCORE__)
