2011-11-11  Gavin Salam  <salam@lpthe.jussieu.fr>

	* include/fastjet/ClusterSequence.hh: 
	* src/ClusterSequence.cc: 
	  moved main page of doxygen documentation into .cc file
	  to avoid big recompilation at every change.

